1.How can I registered for the account?
A: Please contact sales to obtain the account number and initial password provided by Guangdong Vcom Education Technology Co.,Ltd.
2.Types of device and connection control methods

A: User equipment can only be limited to the types of equipment designated by Vcom, and is not compatible with other non-designated equipment types; use Bluetooth and the World Wide Web to connect and control the equipment.

A: The device can restore the device parameter function by switching on and off the power supply, or by deleting the device by software to restore the device function. Note: The Smart scene switch device must be deleted through software to restore the device parameter function.
4.Power on / off mode and result of equipment returning to normal state

A:Operation mode of AC220V power supply on and off for 10 times. \nThe operation process is as follows: first power on, 3 to 5 seconds time range, the device is fully powered on; When the power is cut off again, the equipment will be completely cut off within 3 to 5 seconds. The process of this step needs to be repeated for 10 times, and the equipment can recover the parameter function.
5.App software failed to connect to the device
A: Reconnect by interrupting the power supply 10 times to restore the device parameter function, or restart the Bluetooth function on the phone and re-enter the software to try to connect.
6.When performing automatic search to add a device, the device cannot be searched?
A: Click the scan button to search again, and check whether the device is powered on or proceed to restore the device.
7.Click options in the device list, Unable to enter the device control interface
A: Check whether the current device status is connected or disconnected. In these two states, you cannot enter the device control interface.
